{"type": "article", "id": 28900, "title": "木马椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-30T06:55:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121508Lwrs0xYbejv8aXWD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>意大利设计大师 Enzo Mari 曾在 1974 年设计了一套名为 Autoprogrettazione 家具，人们需要在购买后自己动手把最基础的材料组装起来。最近，首尔的 <a href=\"http://www.jungmoseungyeon.kr/\">Jungmo Seunyeon</a> 工作室就借鉴了 Mari 的设计方针，推出了一套名为 Wooden stable 的座椅。简单明了的木马造型与 DIY 精神联系在了一起，仅依靠锤子和钉子打造。Wooden stable 并不仅限于椅子，可堆叠的设计让它能够根据需要组合成一个支架，放上书籍或是花瓶等物件。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121505JvQRf19SVc5lKD30.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121507aZFYUb7eNvI5LiHK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70904645\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121507c5dvSAUu41RDCVF9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.43031785\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031215079cW1QKdBxqgkrfAm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.30806846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}